---
---

<section id="welcome" class="section">
  <div class="container grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">
    <div class="lg:col-span-6">
      <p class="eyebrow flex items-center" data-reveal><span class="rule"></span>02 / Welcome in</p>
      <h2
        class="display mt-6 text-[clamp(2.4rem,5.6vw,5rem)] text-stage"
        data-headline-split
      >
        We made a place where <em>dance</em> can be the whole <span class="italic text-spotlight">pointe</span> again.
      </h2>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink/80" data-reveal>
        <p>
          Circle City Dance is a brand-new studio in Indianapolis built around a simple belief — that craft and joy aren't a tradeoff. We hold both at once.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our faculty are working artists. Our classrooms are sprung. Our ages run from three-year-olds finding their feet to adults rediscovering theirs. Whatever you're here for — a recital, a reset, a Nutcracker callback, a career — we'll meet you where you are and take you somewhere new.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stage font-display italic text-2xl leading-snug pt-6 border-t border-line">
          Come for the technique. Stay for the people.
        </p>
      </div>

      <ol class="mt-10 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-line border border-line rounded-sm overflow-hidden" data-reveal-stagger>
        <li class="bg-cream p-5" data-reveal-item>
          <div class="font-display italic text-spotlight text-2xl">i.</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/80 leading-snug">
            Small classes. <span class="text-stage/70">No more than the room can teach well.</span>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="bg-cream p-5" data-reveal-item>
          <div class="font-display italic text-spotlight text-2xl">ii.</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/80 leading-snug">
            A real stage every season. <span class="text-stage/70">Lights, theatre, the whole bit.</span>
          </p>
        </li>
        <li class="bg-cream p-5" data-reveal-item>
          <div class="font-display italic text-spotlight text-2xl">iii.</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ink/80 leading-snug">
            Faculty who still perform. <span class="text-stage/70">The field, in the room with you.</span>
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <figure class="lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-8 lg:sticky lg:top-32" data-reveal>
      <div class="relative aspect-[3/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm ring-1 ring-line">
        <img
          src="/images/social/fb-portrait.jpg"
          alt="A vision board on a studio wall — sticky notes from the community sharing dreams for the new dance studio"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 p-5 bg-gradient-to-t from-stage/85 via-stage/40 to-transparent text-cream">
          <div class="text-[0.65rem] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] font-semibold text-rose">From the studio</div>
          <p class="font-display italic text-xl mt-1 leading-snug">"Dream with us. Your ideas matter."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <figcaption class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-stage/50">
        ↳ Our community vision board, opening week
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>
